## ğŸ“‹ Implementation Checklist

When implementing these designs:

### CRITICAL (Do First)
- [ ] Use `Promise.all()` for parallel data fetching in:
  - [ ] Onboarding flow (step 3)
  - [ ] Identity page (all sections)
  - [ ] Chat page (sidebar + messages)
- [ ] Implement direct imports (no barrel files)
- [ ] Add `next/dynamic` for:
  - [ ] BreathAura animation
  - [ ] VibeID radar chart
  - [ ] OAuth buttons
  - [ ] Tool result cards
- [ ] Use React.cache() for shared data fetching

### HIGH Priority
- [ ] Minimize client component serialization
- [ ] Use React Server Components for static sections
- [ ] Implement proper Suspense boundaries at page level

### MEDIUM Priority  
- [ ] Hoist static JSX (tabs, footers, indicators)
- [ ] Use `startTransition` for UI transitions
- [ ] Deduplicate event listeners on mobile

